呼吁苏纳克政府，在英国前首相鲍里斯·约翰逊达成脱欧协议的两年后，重新审视如何改善英国与欧盟的贸易。 有迹象表明，就连一些当初持脱离欧盟立场的人士也开始感到沮丧。英国前环境、食品与农村事务大臣乔治·尤斯蒂斯近期就批评了英国脱欧后与澳大利亚达成的贸易协议，称该协议「付出太多，回报太少」。（来源：环球网） 后悔了？民调：近 2/3 受访英国人支持就是否重新加入欧盟举行公投"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-a8319147215c73a549e3ebf64adb638d_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "20 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/576418363"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I0t3Ou7z9uJ5MEAMaCDkwMzc0NDEwIOHxzZ0GMCQ4tgJAI3IJNTc2NDE4MzYzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "36_1672765646.9116347", "card_id": "Q_574841256", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价王者荣耀 S30 赛季？新版本都有哪些变化？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3f1dc707da517280c79ee01987d17640_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "20 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/574841256"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I0t3Ou7z9uJ5MEAMaCDkwMDI0MDQ5IL3Cpp0GMAA4OEAkcgk1NzQ4NDEyNTZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "37_1672765646.912099", "card_id": "Q_504300910", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 15}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么化妆前不建议敷面膜?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "看过很多完美底妆教程，大部分都有说上妆前建议湿敷而不是敷面膜，但都没有提到为什么"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1e60fd632a76332d64a3e84249159f85_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "19 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/504300910"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I0t3Ou7z9uJ5MEAMaCDc0MzQ3OTE0IJuIvI0GMAA4JkAlcgk1